    <item>
      <title>匈牙利在Orban的支出计划上推到垃圾的边缘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/hungary-pushed-to-edge-of-junk-at-s-p-on-orban-s-spending-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利的主权信用级前景从S＆amp; p全球评级降低到负面，这将国家推向了总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）提高选举前支出后，将国家推向了垃圾的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/hungary-pushed-to-edge-of-junk-at-s-p-on-orban-s-spending-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 21:23:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉升级尼日利亚以援引政策改革的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/fitch-upgrades-nigeria-to-b-citing-commitment-to-policy-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚的信用等级通过惠誉评级升级为B，保留在投机级类别中，理由是提高了政策信誉，并降低了宏观经济稳定性的近期风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/fitch-upgrades-nigeria-to-b-citing-commitment-to-policy-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 21:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
