    <item>
      <title>随着市场沉没并猛增，华尔街散布着新的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/as-markets-sank-and-soared-a-new-fear-spread-across-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当特朗普邮报命中时；真正的一个，而不是骗局＆mdash; S＆amp; P 500在周三的八分钟内跃升了7％，Ed al-Hussainy离开了曼哈顿的桌子。当时，阿尔戈斯（Algos）接管了这一点，买入命令在所有市场上涌入如此愤怒的剪辑，“无事可做”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/as-markets-sank-and-soared-a-new-fear-spread-across-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 20:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
